bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: event
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Unique ID number for the event; date-time string does NOT necessarily equal the date-time that the event actually occurred. Value serves a unique identifier only.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: date_utc
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Date (UTC) when the event occurred. Created from original dateTimeUTC field in YYYYmmdd format.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: time_utc
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Time (UTC) when the event occurred; in hours and minutes (0000 to 2359). Created from original dateTimeUTC field.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: station
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Identification number of the sampling station.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: cast
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Consecutive cast number for the instrument.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: lat
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Latitude in decimal degrees at the time the event occurred. North = positive.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: lon
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Longitude in decimal degrees at the time the event occurred. East = positive.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: author
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Name of person that recorded the event.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: comment
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Comment entered about the sampling event; free-text.

sources.title: Inorganic and organic nutrient data from Niskin bottles from R/V Knorr cruise KN210-04 in the Western Atlantic Ocean between Uruguay and Barbados in 2013 (Deep Atlantic DOM project)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: date_start_utc
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Date (UTC) given as 4-digit year -- 2-digit month -- 2-digit day in YYYYmmdd format.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: event_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: The event number from the ELOG maintained during the cruise.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: lat_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Latitude at the time the event started (from the cruise event log).

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: lon_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Longitude at the time the event started (from the cruise event log).

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: bots
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: The full range of Niskin bottles used for the sample collection. For this particular dataset this is equal to the Niskin number.

sources.title: Processed CTD data from all sensors mounted on the rosette from R/V Knorr cruise KN210-04 in the Western Atlantic Ocean between Uruguay and Barbados in 2013 (Deep Atlantic DOM project)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: date_start_utc
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Date (UTC) given as 4-digit year -- 2-digit month -- 2-digit day in YYYYmmdd format.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: event_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: The event number from the ELOG maintained during the cruise.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: lat_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Latitude at the time the event started (from the cruise event log).

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: lon_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Longitude at the time the event started (from the cruise event log).

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: temp
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Temperature from primary sensor on CTD. (Originally called 't090C'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: temp2
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Temperature from secondary sensor on CTD. (Originally called 't190C'.).

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: sal
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Salinity from primary sensor on CTD. (Originally called 'sal00'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: sal2
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Salinity from secondary sensor on CTD. (Originally called 'sal11'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: density
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Density from primary sensor on CTD. (Originally called 'density00'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: density2
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Density from secondary sensor on CTD. (Originally called 'density11'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: fluor
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Fluorescence from WET Labs ECO-AFL/FL. (Originally called 'flECO_AFL'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: trans
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Beam transmission from WET Labs C-Star. (Originally called 'CStarTr0'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: turbidity
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: Turbidity from WET Labs ECO. (Originally called 'tubWETntu0'.)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: par
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:units: microEinsteins per square meter per second (μE/m2-sec)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: spar
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:units: microEinsteins per square meter per second (μE/m2-sec)

sources.title: Total organic sulfur (TOS) collected from Niskin bottle samples on R/V Knorr cruise KN210-04 in the Western Atlantic Ocean between Uruguay and Barbados from March to May 2013 (Deep Atlantic DOM project)

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: date_utc_YYYYMMDD_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: date, UTC, given as year – month – day

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: time_utc_HHMM_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: time, UTC, given as hour – minute

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: event_start
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: the event number from the ELOG maintained during the cruise

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: TOS_sd
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: standard deviation for total organic sulfur, from averages of replicates where available

sources.title: Sample information for metaproteomic samples taken from Station 2 from R/V Knorr KN210-04 in the Western Atlantic Ocean between Uruguay and Barbados from March 2013

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: ms_ms_sample_name
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: additional sample identifier that includes date of analysis run, method (2D), total amount of protein injected, cruise name, station number, pump cast number, filter type, and sample depth

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: latitude_dd
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: latitude of sampling location with positive values indicating North

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: longitude_dd
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: longitude of sampling location with positive values indicating West

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: date_ISO
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: date of sample collection in ISO format

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: minimum_filter_size_microns
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: minimum filter sized used reported in microns

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: maximum_filter_size_microns
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: maximum filter sized used reported in microns

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: event_number
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: event identification number which includes sampling date in year-month-day format. This ID corresponds to the DeepDOM event log 'event' parameter.

bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:name: ISO_DateTime_UTC
bcodmo:parameters.bcodmo:description: ISO standardized time and date of sampling.
